 red;\">【國際人權日．正日集會】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n</span><br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPK0vx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPK0vx.jpg&h=63585984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀屌你再過7個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n一陣要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"ebc386f9f5883aa45017c30af8d57fe11190eee8","tid":1777061,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"祂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1476cdbc63b442f1f79d7cec9cc447bcf23e5faf","tid":1777061,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"做bot撚啦"},{"pid":"f028ec2966b54e3b14b5493f5fca8bdcd4015916","tid":1777061,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc386f9f5883aa45017c30af8d57fe11190eee8","tid":1777061,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"祂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"法國gay妹份人幾detail<br />\n昂子又幾留意到"},{"pid":"6a6721065995e3fb1b986c636f956d78320be356","tid":1777061,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f028ec2966b54e3b14b5493f5fca8bdcd4015916","tid":1777061,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc386f9f5883aa45017c30af8d57fe11190eee8","tid":1777061,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20